// WORKING NAME: "Purgatory" (cheat death)
// Class: Blood Death Knight
// Slot: passive, reactive (no input binding, no auto-cast)
// Unlock: randomly at level 4/5/6 (band ability, alongside Abomination Limb and AMZ).
//
// Never fires through the normal TriggerAbilityEvent pipeline — this AbilityDef exists only so
// `ability::systems::purgatory::purgatory_cheat_death` can read its (talent-modified) resolved
// params and manage its AbilityCooldown through the same generic tick_ability_cooldowns every
// other ability uses. `behavior: "self_nova"` + `radius: 0.0` is a harmless placeholder in case it
// were ever accidentally triggered (a guaranteed whiff).
(
    id: "purgatory",
    display_name: "Purgatory",
    unlock_schedule: Band(4, 6),
    behavior: "self_nova",
    hooks: [],
    base_params: {
        "radius": 0.0,
        "restore_percent": 5.0,
        "immunity_secs": 5.0,
        "cooldown": 45.0,
    },
    talent_pool: [
        "purgatory_restore_rare",
        "purgatory_immunity_epic",
        "purgatory_cooldown_rare",
    ],
)
